488
00:32:26,644 --> 00:32:28,580
Tidak, tunggu. Tunggu sebentar.

489
00:32:28,613 --> 00:32:30,615
Tunggu, tunggu. Tunggu sebentar.

490
00:32:30,648 --> 00:32:34,451
