01:16:03,227 --> 01:16:05,029
- Omong kosong.

1101
01:16:05,062 --> 01:16:07,098
- Lihat saja.

1102
01:16:49,039 --> 01:16:50,941
- Bagaimana kau
melakukannya, Mike?

