01:22:26,544 --> 01:22:30,047
Nomor tak dikenal?
- Bukan.

1204
01:22:35,319 --> 01:22:38,222
- Pak Balsillie?
- Ya.

1205
01:22:38,255 --> 01:22:40,658
Selamat datang di
Liga Hoki Nasional.

1206
01:22:40,692 --> 01:22:42,426
- Terima kasih telah
mengundangku.

1207
01:22:42,459 --> 01:22:44,027
- Senang bertemu
denganmu. Lewat sini.

1208
01:22:44,061 --> 01:22:45,630
- Baiklah.

1209
01:22:48,766 --> 01:22:50,535
- Di sini.

